Hamilton Lane Private Equity Fund IX LP: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 10:42 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Hamilton Lane Private Equity Fund IX LP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Hamilton Lane Private Equity Fund IX LP specializes in fund of funds and secondaries investments. The fund seeks to invest between 15 to 20 percent of its investments to secondaries; between 40 and 55 percent to buyout; and the remainder in credit, distressed, venture capital, growth, and co-investments in small- to mid-sized funds. It prefers to invest in Europe and the United States.


